            <Abstract ID="Abs1" Language="En">
              <Heading>Abstract</Heading>
              <Para>The remainders and the convergence of cardinal polyharmonic spline interpolation are studied, and the asymptotic behavior of the best approximation by polyharmonic spline and the average<Emphasis Type="Italic">K</Emphasis>-width of some class of smooth functions defined on the Euclidean space<Emphasis Type="Italic">R</Emphasis>
                <Superscript>n</Superscript> are determined.</Para>
            </Abstract>
